                  <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#117v" facs="119">Fol. 117v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1031VirginAndChild">Virgin and Child</ref> with two <term key="angel" ana="#angel"/>s. A patron lays prostrate before them</desc></decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4"><locus target="#118r" facs="119">Fol. 118r</locus><desc>An <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1012Equestrian">Equestrian Saint</ref> holding a spear</desc></decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d5">
                  Decorative designs:
                  <locus target="#1r #6r #12r #18v #27r #33r #37v #45r #53v #59r #63r #71r #78v #80v #81r #85v #90r #100r #105r #106r #117v" facs="002 007 013 020 028 034 039 046 055 060 064 072 080 082 087 091 101 106 107 119">folss. 1r, 6r, 12r, 18v, 27r, 33r, 37v, 45r, 53v, 59r, 63r, 71r, 78v, 80v, 81r, 85v, 90r, 100r, 105r, 106r, 117v, </locus> (ornamental band);
